{"tid":1328436,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(周末好去處) 守護香港行動 撐修例大聯盟周六添馬公園集會","createTime":"2019-07-18T02:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T02:16:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2858c363f581970172fb9252f7cb11f86f165251","tid":1328436,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190716/s00001/cf7255c6de362269a4f205e38d838fab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190716%2Fs00001%2Fcf7255c6de362269a4f205e38d838fab.jpg&h=47dc9d71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（李梓敬fb截圖）<br />\n<br />\n自由黨區議員李梓敬晚上在facebook發帖，指「一班愛香港嘅朋友」，決定本周六（7月20日）下午4時半於添馬公園發起「守護香港大集會」。李梓敬接受查詢時稱，「守護香港行動」籌辦此集會，而他本人幫手宣傳，該集會已申請不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n李梓敬在facebook稱，6月以來每個星期，都不斷有暴力、對峙場面，在不同社區出現；身邊不少朋友，不分政見，都認為「係時候停！係時候令我哋嘅社會回覆（復）安寧！」他表示，舉辦集會是想和平守法地表達希望香港回復安寧的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n李梓敬接受查詢時透露，他原擬同日在維園舉行集會，已申請了不反對通知書，但因保公義撐修例大聯盟亦會舉辦集會，故合併舉辦。至於會否擔心出現早前「撐警集會」不同立場人士衝突場面，李梓敬稱汲取了經驗，會小心，將安排更多糾察和義工，但預料「對家」會挑釁。<br />\n<br />\n保公義撐修例大聯盟由多名港區人大和全國政協委員組成，他們早前發起聯署行動，支持政府修訂《逃犯條例》，稱在6月12日收集約92萬個聯署。政府宣布暫緩修例後，大聯盟發聲明表示理解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190716/s00001/1563286757805/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E4%BC%99%E6%92%90%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E6%B7%BB%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E6%9D%8E%E6%A2%93%E6%95%AC-%E5%90%84%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%8D%E5%B3%99%E3%80%8C%E4%BF%82%E6%99%82%E5%80%99%E5%81%9C%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190716%2Fs00001%2F1563286757805%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25BC%2599%25E6%2592%2590%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%2595%25AC-%25E5%2590%2584%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25B3%2599%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25BF%2582%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2581%259C%25E3%2580%258D&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaaks04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=1f10b4cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190716%2Fs00001%2F1563286757805%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25BC%2599%25E6%2592%2590%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%2595%25AC-%25E5%2590%2584%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25B3%2599%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25BF%2582%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2581%259C%25E3%2580%258D&h=aca6fea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190716/s00001/1563286757805/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E4%BC%99%E6%92%90%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E6%B7%BB%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E6%9D%8E%E6%A2%93%E6%95%AC-%E5%90%84%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%8D%E5%B3%99%E3%80%8C%E4%BF%82%E6%99%82%E5%80%99%E5%81%9C%E3%80%8D</a>"}]}